      "message": "I was referring to the mkdtemp, yes.\n\nIf we can shrink the window in which we can leak the mount, that\u0027s good. I agree that doing cleanup with the current way things are structured is hard, but it\u0027s also true that there are not a lot of features creating new stuff in the FS.\n\nI agree that since we\u0027re creating this inside a new mount namespace, I\u0027m not too worried about it.",
